name: Mejan Home Stay
address: GX26+RQ7 Br Dinas Kutuh, Jl. Pantai Kelating, Majan, Kec. Selemadeg, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82164, Indonesia
review 1:
This Home Stay has to be one of my favorites in Bali so far. The bed is comfortable, the air condition strong, the location is perfect and the owner is incredibly friendly.
Located right next to a rice field and far away enough from the main road this place is quiet and serene. Mejan Beach with its glittering black sand is just a 5 minute walk away, perfect to enjoy that sunset. Balian Beach is also just a 15-20 walk away, or a 3 minute scooter ride.
Putu, the owner, has made this stay memorable with her kind and loving soul, taking great care of the house and it‚Äôs guest alike. Would 100% recommend and stay again!

name: Villa Yuyu Balian
address: Jl. Batu Mejan, Lalanglinggah, Kec. Selemadeg Bar., Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82162, Indonesia
review 1: Best birthday party ever! We spent a fabulous holiday here. The open and serene space is such a hidden gem. Incredibly intimate and private. The friendly and highly professional staff goes out of their way to anticipate and answer our needs. Will recommend!
review 2: Really incredible villa in one of the quieter areas of Bali, close to quiet surf beach with Volcanic sands and awesome seafood. Highly recommended for intimate family or group holidays.
review 4:
This is the third time we have spent a week at Villa JuJu.  There is everything I like here. The beach is 150m away and is mostly deserted and huge.  There are a few restaurants within walking distance but I also like to cook in this open kitchen which overlooks the garden and the swimming pool and it is a real pleasure to shop in the small shops along the main road of the village.  The staff is very nice and especially Wayan who helped us a lot to organize outings.  The +: There are 2 massage benches and the masseuse comes on site.  Ask for Ilu, she's great.
The villa is located in amazing nature, rice fields and lovely cows that look like deer.
We will surely come back.
